How to Use and Contribute

  • Now you are in Awesome Design Plugins section, if you need tools go to Awesome Design Tools.
  • To find the tool, go through the Table of Contents or search for a keyword (for example, "animation", "prototyping").
  • Ask Lisa on Twitter.

If you found some great design tool or plugin, just send a Pull Request concerning our Contribution Guidelines (they're very simple, please take a look). Design tools should be submitted here and plugins in this file. We use such labels for Sketch , Adobe XD and Figma plugins, don't forget to add them. Now I'd love to see your suggestions!

Accessibility

  • S
    Stark
    Sketch
    Figma

    Ensure your design is accessible and high contrast for every type of color blindness.

  • CC
    Color Contrast Analyser
    Sketch

    A Sketch plugin that calculates the color contrast of two selected layers and evaluates it against the WCAG2.0.

  • CC
    Check Contrast
    Sketch

    Allows you to select layers in Sketch and get realtime feedback about the contrast ratio.

  • C
    Contrast
    Sketch

    A Sketch plugin to show a pass/fail type contrast report.

  • SC
    Sketch Color Contrast Analyzer
    Sketch

    A Sketch plugin that calculates the color contrast of two layers and evaluates them against MCOE's guidelines.

  • A-
    A11y - Color Contrast Checker
    Figma

    Ensure your text is readable for users by adhering to WCAG (Web Content Accessibility Guidelines) standards.

  • CB
    Color Blind
    Figma

    It allows you to view your designs in the 8 different types of color vision deficiencies.

  • A
    Able Friction free accessibility
    Figma

    Able makes accessibility easy while looking and feeling like Figma!

  • C
    Contrast
    Figma

    Contrast makes it easy to check the contrast ratios of colors as you work.

  • A-
    A11y - Focus Orderer
    Figma

    Quickly annotate your designs focus/tab order flow. Why? Because not everyone uses a mouse cursor to navigate through online experiences; some people use the keyboard and/or other input devices.

  • A&
    Arabic & RTL Support
    Figma

    Write Arabic and RTL text in Figma with ease.

  • V
    VisualEyes
    Figma

    Measure the attention of your design inside Figma.

  • Rs
    RTL support
    Figma

    Flip RTL languages like Hebrew and Arabic.

  • R-
    RTLPLZ - RTL Support
    Figma

    Write RTL text in Figma with fewer tears.

  • EB
    Epilepsy Blocker
    Figma

    With this plugin you can make your designs accessible and safe for people with photosensitive epilepsy and also stay ADA Compliant.

  • Lt
    LTR to RTL by Alon Gruss
    Adobe XD

    Use Ctrl+h or Cmd+h to flip from LTR text to RTL.

    Generate entire groups of artboards for each experience and device selected with every artboard needed for that specific experience, and defined sizes for the device resolution.
